-- morphism levels before object levels. See note [category_theory universes].
theorem raised_cone_lowers_to_original [IsConnected J] {B : C} {F : «expr ⥤ » J (Over B)}
    (c : Cone («expr ⋙ » F (forget B))) (t : IsLimit c) : (forget B).map_cone (raiseCone c) = c := by tidy
